casebody.data:
Uri Anwar SMALL
v.
NORTH CAROLINA DIVISION OF PRISONS; Jennie Lancaster; and Benny Langdon. No. 41P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 3, 2005. Uri Small, Pro Se. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, for N.C. Division of Prisons.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 19th day of January 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of February 2005."
